nodes.bodyText: IIUC, the data is being sent from Source FhirStore to Destination FhirStore by the Fhir service itself, right? And we're just managing the Operation on the Dataflow side. Is that correct?
I think we should rename this to Export since GCS is an implementation detail here. Feel free to leave it to a follow-up PR.
